The paper deals with visual tracking, which is a subfield of computer vision (CV). The proposed algorithm uses Compressed Sensing (CS) to accelerate the tracking process, which falls under the category of machine learning (LG) and mathematical modeling (MM). The paper also discusses dimensionality reduction and signal recovery, which are topics in information theory (IT) and signal processing (SI). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IT, and cs.SI.
